The reduction will be even greater - it is estimated that one in four sinisters would be avoided with damage to people - when the so-called emergency braking intelligent systems are popularized.
In this case, the vehicle is equipped with a system that (through a radar or camera) detects the obstacles and warns the driver, as well as acts slightly on the brakes.
